[[!ftemplate id=tool]]

Components:

- Platform:
   - Description: The web application that pulls together all the components of DocumentCloud
   - Source: <https://github.com/documentcloud/documentcloud>
- Document viewer
   - Description: Allows for the display of images and text from documents.
   - Source: <https://github.com/documentcloud/document-viewer>
- Notes
    - Description: Provides a tool to highlight regions of the document images
    - Source: <https://github.com/documentcloud/documentcloud-notes>
- Visual Search
    - Description: Search boxes with facets and autocompletion
    - Homepage: <http://documentcloud.github.io/visualsearch/>
    - Source: <https://github.com/documentcloud/visualsearch>
